{
  "code": 200,
  "status": "OK",
  "data": {
    "number": 54,
    "name": "سُورَةُ القَمَرِ",
    "englishName": "Al-Qamar",
    "englishNameTranslation": "The Moon",
    "revelationType": "Meccan",
    "numberOfAyahs": 55,
    "ayahs": [
      {
        "number": 4847,
        "text": "The Hour has drawn near and the moon is split.",
        "numberInSurah": 1,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 528,
        "ruku": 463,
        "hizbQuarter": 211,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4848,
        "text": "If they see a sign, they turn away, and say, ‘An incessant magic!’",
        "numberInSurah": 2,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 528,
        "ruku": 463,
        "hizbQuarter": 211,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4849,
        "text": "They denied and followed their own desires, and every matter has a setting [appropriate to it].",
        "numberInSurah": 3,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 528,
        "ruku": 463,
        "hizbQuarter": 211,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4850,
        "text": "There have already come to them reports containing admonishment,",
        "numberInSurah": 4,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 528,
        "ruku": 463,
        "hizbQuarter": 211,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4851,
        "text": "[and representing] far-reaching wisdom; but warnings are of no avail!",
        "numberInSurah": 5,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 528,
        "ruku": 463,
        "hizbQuarter": 211,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4852,
        "text": "So turn away from them! The day when the Caller calls to a dire thing,",
        "numberInSurah": 6,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 528,
        "ruku": 463,
        "hizbQuarter": 211,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4853,
        "text": "they will emerge from the graves as if they were scattered locusts with a humbled look [in their eyes],",
        "numberInSurah": 7,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 529,
        "ruku": 463,
        "hizbQuarter": 211,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4854,
        "text": "scrambling toward the summoner. The faithless will say, ‘This is a hard day!’",
        "numberInSurah": 8,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 529,
        "ruku": 463,
        "hizbQuarter": 211,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4855,
        "text": "The people of Noah impugned before them. So they impugned Our servant and said, ‘A crazy man,’ and he was reviled.",
        "numberInSurah": 9,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 529,
        "ruku": 463,
        "hizbQuarter": 212,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4856,
        "text": "Thereat he invoked his Lord, [saying,] ‘I have been overcome, so help [me].’",
        "numberInSurah": 10,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 529,
        "ruku": 463,
        "hizbQuarter": 212,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4857,
        "text": "Then We opened the gates of the sky with pouring waters,",
        "numberInSurah": 11,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 529,
        "ruku": 463,
        "hizbQuarter": 212,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4858,
        "text": "and We made the earth burst forth with springs, and the waters met for a preordained purpose.",
        "numberInSurah": 12,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 529,
        "ruku": 463,
        "hizbQuarter": 212,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4859,
        "text": "We bore him on a vessel made of planks and nails,",
        "numberInSurah": 13,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 529,
        "ruku": 463,
        "hizbQuarter": 212,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4860,
        "text": "which sailed [over the flood waters] in Our sight, as a retribution for him who was met with disbelief.",
        "numberInSurah": 14,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 529,
        "ruku": 463,
        "hizbQuarter": 212,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4861,
        "text": "Certainly We have left it as a sign; so is there anyone who will be admonished?",
        "numberInSurah": 15,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 529,
        "ruku": 463,
        "hizbQuarter": 212,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4862,
        "text": "So how were My punishment and warnings?",
        "numberInSurah": 16,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 529,
        "ruku": 463,
        "hizbQuarter": 212,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4863,
        "text": "Certainly We have made the Quran simple for the sake of admonishment. So is there anyone who will be admonished?",
        "numberInSurah": 17,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 529,
        "ruku": 463,
        "hizbQuarter": 212,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4864,
        "text": "[The people of] ‘Ad impugned [their apostle]. So how were My punishment and warnings?",
        "numberInSurah": 18,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 529,
        "ruku": 463,
        "hizbQuarter": 212,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4865,
        "text": "Indeed We unleashed upon them an icy gale on an incessantly ill-fated day,",
        "numberInSurah": 19,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 529,
        "ruku": 463,
        "hizbQuarter": 212,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4866,
        "text": "knocking down people as if they were trunks of uprooted palm trees.",
        "numberInSurah": 20,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 529,
        "ruku": 463,
        "hizbQuarter": 212,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4867,
        "text": "So how were My punishment and warnings?!",
        "numberInSurah": 21,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 529,
        "ruku": 463,
        "hizbQuarter": 212,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4868,
        "text": "Certainly We have made the Quran simple for the sake of admonishment. So is there anyone who will be admonished?",
        "numberInSurah": 22,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 529,
        "ruku": 463,
        "hizbQuarter": 212,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4869,
        "text": "[The people of] Thamud denied the warnings,",
        "numberInSurah": 23,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 529,
        "ruku": 464,
        "hizbQuarter": 212,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4870,
        "text": "and they said, ‘Are we to follow a lone human from ourselves?! Indeed then we would be in error and madness.’",
        "numberInSurah": 24,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 529,
        "ruku": 464,
        "hizbQuarter": 212,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4871,
        "text": "‘Has the Reminder been cast upon him from among us? No, he is a self-conceited liar.’",
        "numberInSurah": 25,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 529,
        "ruku": 464,
        "hizbQuarter": 212,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4872,
        "text": "‘Tomorrow they will know who is a self-conceited liar.",
        "numberInSurah": 26,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 529,
        "ruku": 464,
        "hizbQuarter": 212,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4873,
        "text": "We are sending the She-camel as a trial for them; so watch them and be steadfast.",
        "numberInSurah": 27,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 529,
        "ruku": 464,
        "hizbQuarter": 212,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4874,
        "text": "Inform them that the water is to be shared between them; each of them showing up at his turn.’",
        "numberInSurah": 28,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 530,
        "ruku": 464,
        "hizbQuarter": 212,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4875,
        "text": "But they called their companion, and he took [a knife] and hamstrung [her].",
        "numberInSurah": 29,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 530,
        "ruku": 464,
        "hizbQuarter": 212,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4876,
        "text": "So how were My punishment and My warnings?!",
        "numberInSurah": 30,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 530,
        "ruku": 464,
        "hizbQuarter": 212,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4877,
        "text": "We sent against them a single Cry, and they became like the dry sticks of a corral builder.",
        "numberInSurah": 31,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 530,
        "ruku": 464,
        "hizbQuarter": 212,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4878,
        "text": "Certainly We have made the Quran simple for the sake of admonishment. So is there anyone who will be admonished?",
        "numberInSurah": 32,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 530,
        "ruku": 464,
        "hizbQuarter": 212,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4879,
        "text": "And the people of Lot denied the warnings.",
        "numberInSurah": 33,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 530,
        "ruku": 464,
        "hizbQuarter": 212,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4880,
        "text": "We unleashed upon them a rain of stones, excepting the family of Lot, whom We delivered at dawn",
        "numberInSurah": 34,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 530,
        "ruku": 464,
        "hizbQuarter": 212,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4881,
        "text": "as a blessing from Us. Thus do We reward those who give thanks.",
        "numberInSurah": 35,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 530,
        "ruku": 464,
        "hizbQuarter": 212,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4882,
        "text": "He had already warned them of Our punishment, but they disputed the warnings.",
        "numberInSurah": 36,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 530,
        "ruku": 464,
        "hizbQuarter": 212,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4883,
        "text": "They even solicited of him his guests, whereat We blotted out their eyes, [saying,] ‘Taste My punishment and My warnings!’",
        "numberInSurah": 37,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 530,
        "ruku": 464,
        "hizbQuarter": 212,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4884,
        "text": "Early at dawn there visited them an abiding punishment:",
        "numberInSurah": 38,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 530,
        "ruku": 464,
        "hizbQuarter": 212,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4885,
        "text": "‘Taste My punishment and warnings!’",
        "numberInSurah": 39,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 530,
        "ruku": 464,
        "hizbQuarter": 212,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4886,
        "text": "Certainly We have made the Quran simple for the sake of admonishment. So is there anyone who will be admonished?",
        "numberInSurah": 40,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 530,
        "ruku": 464,
        "hizbQuarter": 212,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4887,
        "text": "Certainly the warnings did come to Pharaoh’s clan",
        "numberInSurah": 41,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 530,
        "ruku": 465,
        "hizbQuarter": 212,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4888,
        "text": "who denied all of Our signs. So We seized them with the seizing of One [who is] all-mighty, Omnipotent.",
        "numberInSurah": 42,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 530,
        "ruku": 465,
        "hizbQuarter": 212,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4889,
        "text": "Are your faithless better than those? Have you [been granted] [some sort of] immunity in the scriptures?",
        "numberInSurah": 43,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 530,
        "ruku": 465,
        "hizbQuarter": 212,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4890,
        "text": "Do they say, ‘We are a confederate league’?",
        "numberInSurah": 44,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 530,
        "ruku": 465,
        "hizbQuarter": 212,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4891,
        "text": "The league will be routed and turn its back [to flee].",
        "numberInSurah": 45,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 530,
        "ruku": 465,
        "hizbQuarter": 212,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4892,
        "text": "Indeed, the Hour is their tryst; and the Hour will be most calamitous and bitter.",
        "numberInSurah": 46,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 530,
        "ruku": 465,
        "hizbQuarter": 212,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4893,
        "text": "Indeed the guilty are steeped in error and madness.",
        "numberInSurah": 47,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 530,
        "ruku": 465,
        "hizbQuarter": 212,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4894,
        "text": "The day when they are dragged on their faces into the Fire, [it will be said to them,] ‘Taste the touch of hell!’",
        "numberInSurah": 48,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 530,
        "ruku": 465,
        "hizbQuarter": 212,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4895,
        "text": "Indeed We have created everything in a measure,",
        "numberInSurah": 49,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 530,
        "ruku": 465,
        "hizbQuarter": 212,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4896,
        "text": "and Our command is but a single [word], like the twinkling of an eye.",
        "numberInSurah": 50,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 531,
        "ruku": 465,
        "hizbQuarter": 212,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4897,
        "text": "Certainly We have destroyed your likes. So is there anyone who will be admonished?",
        "numberInSurah": 51,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 531,
        "ruku": 465,
        "hizbQuarter": 212,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4898,
        "text": "Everything they have done is in the books,",
        "numberInSurah": 52,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 531,
        "ruku": 465,
        "hizbQuarter": 212,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4899,
        "text": "and everything big and small is committed to writing.",
        "numberInSurah": 53,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 531,
        "ruku": 465,
        "hizbQuarter": 212,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4900,
        "text": "Indeed the Godwary will be amid gardens and streams,",
        "numberInSurah": 54,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 531,
        "ruku": 465,
        "hizbQuarter": 212,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4901,
        "text": "in the abode of truthfulness with an omnipotent King.",
        "numberInSurah": 55,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 531,
        "ruku": 465,
        "hizbQuarter": 212,
        "sajda": false
      }
    ],
